6540.text: [6540] StaticText '🪄 Agent Lumos: Unified and Modular Training for Open-Source Language Agents'

6576.text: [6576] StaticText ' unifies a suite of complex interactive tasks and achieves competitive performance with GPT-4/3.5-based and larger open-source agents.'

6598.text: [6598] StaticText ' consists of planning, grounding, and execution modules built based on LLAMA-2-7B/13B and off-the-shelf APIs.'

6605.text: [6605] StaticText ' utilizes a unified data format that encompasses multiple task types, thereby enabling the developed agent framework to conveniently support a range of interactive tasks.'

6622.text: [6622] StaticText ' is trained with ~56K diverse high-quality subgoal/action annotations from ground-truth reasoning steps in existing benchmarks with GPT-4.'
